<%#
  Severity dot. Locals:
    severity (String) — "critical" / "warning" / "cleared"
    status   (String) — "firing" / "acknowledged" / "cleared" (drives pulse)
  The pulse only fires for firing + critical (the deliberate high-impact
  moment). Every other combination is a static colored dot.
%>
<span class="alarm-dot alarm-dot--<%= severity %> alarm-dot--<%= status %>"
      aria-label="<%= severity.to_s.titleize %> severity, <%= status.to_s.titleize %>">
</span>
